<paragraph base="F55750834" id="IFRS17_BC9"><paranum>BC9</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 17"/><data name="paranum" value="BC9"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS17_P5772">Insurance contracts are excluded from the scope of many existing IFRS Standards that might otherwise apply to such contracts, including Standards on:</p><ol base="F55750836" id="IFRS17_L0419" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p base="F55750837" id="IFRS17_P5773">revenue (see <xref base="F59357461" href="../ifrs14/IFRS15_TOC.dita#IFRS15_TOC0001/IFRS15_TOC0001_V2" id="IFRS17_X1362"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IFRS 15</ph> <ph outputclass="standard_title">Revenue from Contracts with Customers</ph></ph></xref>);</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p base="F55750840" id="IFRS17_P5774">liabilities (see <xref base="F59357462" href="../ias37/IAS37_TOC.dita#IAS37_TOC0001" id="IFRS17_X1363"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IAS 37</ph> <ph outputclass="standard_title">Provisions, Contingent Liabilities and Contingent Assets</ph></ph></xref>); and</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p base="F55750843" id="IFRS17_P5775">financial instruments (see <xref base="F70527839" href="../ifrs09/IFRS09_TOC.dita#IFRS09_TOC0001" id="IFRS17_X1364"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IFRS 9</ph> <ph outputclass="standard_title">Financial Instruments</ph></ph></xref> and <xref base="F59357464" href="../ias32/IAS32_TOC.dita#IAS32_TOC0001/IAS32_TOC0001_V2" id="IFRS17_X1365"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IAS 32</ph> <ph outputclass="standard_title">Financial Instruments: Presentation</ph></ph></xref>).</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>